{"id": 864, "genre": 1001, "title": "有关办公环境，你有什么想吐槽的？", "description": "我想建议公司在办公室里装个意见箱，然而始终找不到提议的途径。 ——Liquors", "record_count": 3602, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183711jKQZrRCOzwnJlG4e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-17T11:06:13Z", "options": [{"id": 66048, "content": "部门墙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561359}, {"id": 59136, "content": "空调太凉", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347080}, {"id": 59137, "content": "没有休闲杂志角", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519721}, {"id": 59138, "content": "男的不洗澡，脚臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347080}, {"id": 59139, "content": "不通风、空间太小、密闭感强烈、办公桌逼格太低", "image": null, "praise_count": 320, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486532}, {"id": 74244, "content": "空调太冷、空调太热....永远调不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595067}, {"id": 59140, "content": "办公桌的柜子被封死，不允许放东西到柜子里，只好把东西全摆在桌面上", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236950}, {"id": 59141, "content": "桌子太小太拥挤", "image": null, "praise_count": 129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123452}, {"id": 59142, "content": "桌子太小太拥挤", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123452}, {"id": 59912, "content": "我的办公室是在仓库里……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524425}, {"id": 59145, "content": "我的座位风水太差了", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519740}, {"id": 59146, "content": "说好的办公室PLAY呢？意淫了那么久就给我看这种办公室！人也太多了吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506043}, {"id": 59147, "content": "我有好多好多的东西没地方放！", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462008}, {"id": 59148, "content": "不禁烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 185, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59573}, {"id": 59149, "content": "总有人能看到你的电脑屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 658, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238743}, {"id": 60173, "content": "连个茶水间都没有，更不要提咖啡饮料了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512571}, {"id": 59150, "content": "手机没信号，网速慢，空气差，冬天热死，夏天冷死，广告公司比较自由，但是被迫听各种音乐也是醉了，插个耳机会死吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426712}, {"id": 59406, "content": "噪音噪音", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502682}, {"id": 59151, "content": "厕所排风不好，特别臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498282}, {"id": 59407, "content": "禁烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502682}, {"id": 59152, "content": "没有食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508296}, {"id": 59153, "content": "没有阳台 阳台可以打电话 吃东西 透气有没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518297}, {"id": 67858, "content": "空调，夏天冷气吹不到，冬天噪声很大但没卵用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565486}, {"id": 59154, "content": "完全开放的办公环境，超强的白帜灯光，感觉喝水声音都很大…尴尬症越来越严重了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256865}, {"id": 59155, "content": "网络也属于办公环境的内容？网慢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 223, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 59156, "content": "马勒戈壁?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517587}, {"id": 59157, "content": "周边环境污染空气有毒 用生命在换钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496813}, {"id": 59158, "content": "就是设计感不够重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517151}, {"id": 59159, "content": "空间不够自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 59160, "content": "没有私人空间，自己电脑要和同事共享。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518114}, {"id": 59161, "content": "某会办公环境就像上世纪末的网吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519806}, {"id": 59162, "content": "请把铃声是江南Style，电话随时会打入，音量有60dB的手机随时带在身边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167762}, {"id": 59163, "content": "请把铃声是江南Style，电话随时会打入，音量有60dB的手机随时带在身边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167762}, {"id": 59164, "content": "秘书苏", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519810}, {"id": 59165, "content": "椅子很舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256068}, {"id": 59166, "content": "你把ta当朋友 ta把你当对手", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513037}, {"id": 59422, "content": "可以在家里上班吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515742}, {"id": 61214, "content": "办公室还是老式的水泥地板，自带起灰功能怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531071}, {"id": 59167, "content": "艰苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 60448, "content": "中间不设隔板，总跟对面的人互相踢脚?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527535}, {"id": 59169, "content": "要是有专人打扫就好了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519825}, {"id": 59170, "content": "没有茶水间，别提咖啡了，我要咖啡机", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393060}, {"id": 59171, "content": "椅子和桌子的高矮比例总是不合适，办公桌的键盘档为啥总是在下面的抽屉位置，腿都抬不起来，桌子也没有踮脚的横枨", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519839}, {"id": 59172, "content": "光线和空气", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161438QaPnYFEk4VW5Xwqy.png", "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346967}, {"id": 59684, "content": "空气不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346842}, {"id": 63268, "content": "桌面上的笔经常不翼而飞，拿绳子拴在脖子上结果绳子和笔一起消失了，的亏脖子还在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542164}, {"id": 59173, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106835}, {"id": 59174, "content": "太开放了，中午睡觉一直被吵的睡不着，本来休息时间就少", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 59686, "content": "座椅太LOW", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522778}, {"id": 59175, "content": "在家办公；）", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224678}]}